Long time no see LET! 
 
You asked for it?  We have it!  Catalyst now provides KVM!  We’ve got a fantastic line started up and we’re planning on continuing our quality of support and services you’ve loved!
 
For those of you guys who don’t know us, Catalyst Host was started by Ryan Arp (@ryanarp ) and the Jarland Donnell (@jarland ) focused on providing our brand of hosting.  We just want you all to know that we’re more than just another provider, we are customers too.  We know what customers want, and we focus on exactly that!  Just letting you all know, we’re also Catalyst customers ourselves!  We want the best out of everything we get, and we’ll work hard to make sure you get the best we can give!  
 
We’d just like to thank our loyal customers for helping us become where we are now!  
 
